HEADWORD: By-street
<hw>By"-street`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A separate,
private, or obscure street; an out of the way or cross street.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He seeks <qex>by-streets</qex>, and saves the expensive coach.</q>
<rj><qau>Gay.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

